address.streetAddress: Chestnut B Plan, The Reserve At Moore's Dairy

location.fullValue: Chestnut B Plan, The Reserve At Moore's Dairy

data.description: Back on the market! Welcome to this stunning home built in 2012 in Rose Garden Subdivision.  In a community with working adults, this 3 bd 2 ba home is something worth looking at. Entering the home, you have a cozy feeling that leaves a sense of relaxation.  It has an open-floor plan with updated appliances that will be purchased with the home.  The kitchen has ceramic tile.  Therefore, if you are a kitchen person, you will love the open space where you can still watch your favorite movie or sport show while you're cooking. After cooking, you can relax in your luxurious living room which provides a large area that a huge family can enjoy each other and discuss their day.  After you're ready for bed, go in and enjoy the spacious bedrooms with walk-in closets that everyone will enjoy with enough storage space for all. The master bathroom provides dual vanities with two separate closets. New paint has been completed throughout the house. Seller is eager to sell.
